# GitHub Personal Access Token for sandbox containers.
# Create a fine-grained PAT at: https://github.com/settings/personal-access-tokens/new
#
# Recommended permissions (scoped to the repos you work with):
#   - Contents: Read and Write    (clone, push, pull)
#   - Pull requests: Read and Write (read/create/comment on PRs)
#   - Issues: Read                (read issues for context)
#   - Metadata: Read              (always required)
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your token:
SANDBOX_GITHUB_TOKEN=github_pat_...
